Oreos is an old friend from as long as I can remember. They were not available for years when I lived abroad. I can remember the time the grocery had a few tiny packages of Oreos. That was wonderful—a taste of home!  Now I can buy these big family packages of Oreos whenever I wish.  They never change.  Same delicious chocolate cookies with creamy filings. I don’t know how old are Oreos but I know how old I am and can remember enjoying them in the 1930’s.  I still eat them the same way - open them and eat one side at a time. Maybe lick off some of the filling first.  Brings out the inner child.

These portion control packs of Oreos contain 4 cookie sandwiches with a 1.75 inch diameter.  The whole pack is 210 calories, 180 mg. of sodium and 18g of sugars including high fructose corn syrup.I was quite surprised to find that these are vegan so, although I got these for my husband, I was able to try them for myself.  Although I haven’t had Oreos since I was very young, they taste exactly how I remember them.  However, my tastes have changed and I find them to be too sweet and the texture too sticky for my adult palate.  They do generate a lot of crumbs.My husband enjoys these and likes the sweeter taste but I can’t help but wish that they were a bit healthier and would prefer seeing real sugar as an ingredient rather than the high fructose corn syrup.  He considers them as 5 star product while I give them only 3,  so our average rating is 4 stars.

Like most humans, I of course love Oreos. That means a regular size package can get demolished in pretty short order, bad news for my butt. The little packages compensate for my wavering willpower. They’re big enough to share without feeling cheated, but not so big (6pack) you feel remorseful if you eat them all yourself, nor so skimpy you end up eating several, like they’re Halloween candy (2-pack).Since moderation is much easier to impose upon others, I prefer the two packs for my little kids lunch, but the four packs are great for adults, or for sharing with my kiddo has a treat.Of course, I always feel a little rotten about the packaging waste with this sort of thing. Sigh.

I am eating a package as I type this review.  YUM!!!! or YUMMY!!!!  You take your pick.  These are the traditional original OREO cookies.  There are 4 cookies in each package.  I wish there were 40 cookies in each package but my doctor told me I do not need to eat that many in one sitting.  The buy date on these were Jan 2020.  There will NOT be any left by then.  These are fresh and very good.  The packages we have opened have all been good.  No broken ones yet.  The shipping has something to be desired.  The box was a little crushed and I was worried about the cookies being crumbs.  But these Oreo’s are whole and delicious.  OREO is the best.  Love um.

My kids love junk food (what kids don't), but they have a tendency to eat way more in a sitting than they should.  Because of this, I often buy things that are individually wrapped in hopes of teaching them more about portion size.1. The package arrived in great condition.  The vast majority of the cookies were intact and unbroken.2. The cookies were fresh and not stale at all.3. I loved that one pack was a single serving size.  When I saw that they contained four cookies, I worried that there would be two servings per packet (i.e. twice the calories, fat, etc.), but each pack is one serving.  This also helps with my goal of teaching serving sizes to my kids too.4. The box has 30 individual packs of cookies, so it is a really nice size box.Overall, I was very pleased with this order and will definitely order again.

I've been successfully dieting for about 6 months but don't deny myself any fun choices.  What I've learned is portion control.  These 4 packs of oreo cookies are perfect for me.  I can have my snack without eating an entire bag or box.  Oreos are my guilty pleasure and have been for as long as I can remember.  Chocolaty and creamy - yumm.  These are a good choice for the kids too.

Both of my kids love these snack packs. There favorite oreos is double stuff but usually I only let them have two double stuff so they get a little bit more in this snack pack and just gobble them all up. I had this box in my office and even my coworkers couldn't help themselves to some of these snack packs...I had to hide it from them. They are fresh/crunchy, haven't had too many broken ones.

I am hooked on keeping single serve snacks on hand as opposed to larger bags of cookies and chips. While it may be pricier up front, the snacks stay fresher longer and are easier to grab on the go. The single serve packs of Oreo cookies arrived intact with no breakage or crumbled cookies. And four cookies per pack is the perfect snack size and helps with portion control. Perfect for family picnics and church and community gatherings.

These packs are the perfect size for a snack or to pack in lunchboxes. My children love these cookies but a large open package always present a problem in that they eat way more than they should. These packs are perfectly portioned and always fresh. This product eliminates the problem of over eating cookies. A family favorite in convenient packages.

What's to say? Rip a pack open. Separate the cookies and, depending on who you are, eat the cream filled side first OR hold out and eat the cookie side first. Up to you. These are just as delicious as any other Oreo you have eaten?

Honestly, maybe a bit much for an elementary school kid, but whatever -- they can trade a couple away for something else, or it's great to have one pack and share between my two little kids (or with Mom and Dad, too, since four Oreos can easily be shared by a family of four).I'm even happy about the box they come in. The little individual sleeves are stacked neatly in a thin box (like the sort of box for a 12-pack of soda), with no wasted space. It fits neatly in my cupboard, and when it's gone it's easy to break down and recycle without an overabundance of trash.
What's not to like about this legendary cookie? Melts in your mouth, great with glass of milk.

My favorite cookie my family loves them they are creamy and chocolatey they are the best dunked in milk just wish they were less calories lol
My husband loves these! They have to be the double stuff because the cream is the best part. These are a must have desert with a tall glass of milk.
My son’s favorite cookie! He loves the double stuff. I always have to get a pack just for him. He lives to just sit and dip them in milk.

While I am a chocolate lover, I prefer the original filling over the chocolate. It's just a preference and I would also like to note that I'm not a big fan of other flavored Oreos. If you like the other flavors, then give the chocolate a chance.
These are my absolute favorite Oreos!! I have these with a cold class of milk, which is my favorite!! I’ve also made Oreo truffles using the double stuff!!
Double stuff Oreos are the bomb!! They're full of double cream with the same great Oreo chocolate cookie!! Try them there amazing!!
I love double stuffed Oreos. I think when they have more of the cream inside they taste better and can be eaten alone. Regular Oreos are made for dipping in milk.

I think everyone I know has tried a oreo cookie at least once, so you know that the double stuff oreos are so good! But, if you can eat them and haven't tried them, where have you been? lol They're so good. That's why there are so many varieties! And why you see oreos in everything! Try one!
Double stuff is the way to go! Love how creamy the center is and since they are double there is no need to stack 2 regular Oreos on top like I used to
Double stuffed oreos are my favorite snack. It's probably my go to. They even have a gluten free one that's extremely good too.
My favorite oreo is double stuff. My favorite go to snack. My child loves dunking in milk as s acknowledged choice. I love oreo plain
These have been a favorite of mine since childhood and I absolutely love the devil soft even more than the original they are so delicious
I have always loved oreos. All kinds. I dont get them often but when I do I love dipping them in some milk. My husband and son love them too
Good would break it apart to eat the inside first. With milk on the side. Late night snack. It taste so good when you dipped in the milk.
What's better than an Oreo? I don't know these are definitely a hit in our house and my little cookie monster and big cookie monster eat them like they are going out of style
I absolutely love these over all the other Oreos out there if only they had a triple stuff that would be even better. There is no cookie better than an Oreo

It seems as the years go by the filling is getting less and less in these cookies. Double stuf feels more like regular stuf to me. Obviously they’re a classic and they’re tasty but I feel like I’m getting a bit ripped off.
This is the perfect snack for anytime of day. The double stuff is the perfect compliment to the 2 cookies. I couldn’t stop eating after just one.
Sometimes I like to have sweetness in my mouth. Tioi tried it and it feels great. The fusion of cake and ice cream melts in your mouth . I like
These are my guilty pleasure! I have been doing so well on my diet but I have a huge sweet tooth … I will eat one or 2 of these to curb my sweet tooth! So good!
Oreo double stuff is very sweet but good with a glass of milk. It's a nice crisp cookie with a sweet filling. Highly recommended.
The go-to cookie for those sad nights, the period cramps, the lonely woes, the sisters and misters, the everything and anytime.
My go to snack, I literally always have a pack of Oreos in my home and ofc milk! Cannot go wrong with this snack!!!!!!!!!
My favorite type of Oreo! They’re great to just throw in for a snack or for lunches. Easy to take on trips/ hikes! Delicious!
Dbl stuff Oreos are the best ! Can’t go wrong with dbl stuff ! Does anyone else eat there Oreos in peanut butter ?? 😝😝
I would eat these all the time as a child! My family would buy 2-3 packs at a time because my sister would eat them all. I personally like to have them as a small snack and I ALWAYS dip them in milk
Still a classic. Either with milk or without they are still one of the most easily recognizable flavors from childhood.
Oreos are just one of those snacks that can’t be replicated! I love the double stuffed and I have such fond memories of Oreos! They’re best dunked in milk!
I love being able to take the Oreo apart & enjoying each part separately, you get double the cookies then!! They go great with a cold glass of milk!
I love these Oreos! I always thought they would be better with more cream in them and they definitely are!! I definitely recommend this if you think Oreos needs more cream too!
I love the double stuffed Oreo Cookies 😋 They are my family's favorite. I would most definitely recommend this product to everyone. 💞
We always have to have Oreos in stock in this household! We love the flavor and pairing them with milk is the best! All the members of this family choose Oreos over everything! 🙌🏼
Of course double the cream is always better.... The originals are better for things like dirt cake though of course unless u eat the cream out first haha
I love the double stuff oreos. They are so creamy and taste good dunked in milk. Love these cookies. I love regular oreos but these are so much more tasty.
These are a pantry staple! A delicious midnight snack to wash down with a cool glass of milk. Double stuffed, of course.
My family loves Oreos. My kids will eat their veggies for some Oreos as dessert. The packaging is convenient in helping th keep fresh.
We all know and live oreos it is as basic and American as Apple pie, but only better. Too bad they are made with such crap, I guess that's why they taste so good.
Ever since I tried the double stuff oreo I have never purchased the original one. The best part is when you dip them in milk and let them soak. 😋
These are my hubby and kids go to snack. They absolutely love these with a glass of milk. The price is always good on them and the product never changes
I already love Oreos. With these you get double the good stuff in the middle! They’re perfect to break apart into two pieces and lick the middle or to dunk in milk!
I love these cookies especially when you eat them with milk. So delicious. Defiantly recommend it. It’s worth your money.
The double stuff is not worth the hassle of the money. I feel like these have way ti much cream in them per cookie ratio.
These are a classic cookie that can be enjoyed for any occasion. Certainly need some milk to dip in to add to the enjoyment of the cookie.

Nothing like a original Oreo cookie with double stuffed icing. Great to dip in milk by itself or even make a at home milk shake. It so weird how foods, smells, places, etc can bring back memories you forgot even existed. I’ve always loved Oreos and if by some miracle you haven’t tried them then it’s definitely worth a try.

We like to purchase Oreos from time to time. Who doesn't love a good cookie. We sometimes make the easy Oreo cake in a cup. All you need is like 5 to 6 oreos a zip lock baggie and a rolling pin/ something heavy. Put the Oreos in the bag close it then smash the Oreos. Grab your favorite mug dump the oreos in and add some milk to make a batter consistency. Take the cup to microwave cook. Then cool and eat.

I've always loved these cookies but i have a weakness for the double stuff!! Also it's a bonus to have it be vegan and i have a dairy allergy to always keep in mind. I have yet to meet someone who doesn't like these!!

Oreos are sooo good. And double stuff is even better. We all love Oreos in our household for a snack or small dessert. The chocolate taste is classic and the stuffing remains sweet and delicious. Love them!
I loved everything about these. I can lick some off and leave some with cookie. Great taste of right amount of the cream and the chocolate
I love these types of Oreos because if you’re using them for baking, they make the best Oreo balls. You don’t have to use as much cream cheese!
I love Oreos but the last double stuf that I had didn’t seem to have extra cream. But Oreos will always be a childhood favorite.
double stuffed is always superior. It has more cream which makes it more richer and delicious when eaten or dipped in milk.
On rare occasion, I purchase these for my kids. They love to take them apart and make their own version of Oreo cookies!
Who doesn't love Nabisco Oreos? But add in some extra cream and yum. Love all oreo products, but double stuf are a household favorite.
I love Oreos but the double stuf is perfect for people who love the filling more than the cookie! Always best with milk.
Such a classic cookie and so so good. I love getting Oreo ice cream and crushing up a few of these to add more flavor in it
I love Oreos! I like them even better fried! You just dunk them in pancake batter and throw them in hot oil wait until golden. Remove and throw some powdered sugar on them! Ahhh!

I bought this because I love Toblerone Swiss Chocolate bars and wanted to try the new Crunchy Salted Caramelized Almond one. Sighs. Ok, here we go.5 stars for the tried and true Toblerone Swiss Chocolate. It is SO good!3.5 stars for the White Chocolate. It was good, but as white chocolate is sometimes too sweet so was this bar. Also, it's white chocolate.  ¯\_(ツ)_/¯2 stars for the Crunchy Salted Caramelized Almond. Why you ask? I checked the page for these before I purchased them to look at the ingredients. Nowhere in the image for the Nutrition Facts does it say that this bar has wheat in it. I was thrilled so I purchased. When I opened the package I noticed that this bar has ingredients listed on it rather than on the larger packaging. It contains wheat, which I am unable to eat. I ate one anyway, just in case. Oy vey. This one would totally be my favorite if the wheat hadn't made me so ill. Yes, that is my fault for eating it, so if you don't have a wheat allergy have at it.I would not have purchased this if the outside packaging had listed wheat in the first place. Since the wheat made me so ill I ended up giving the rest of the chocolate away to a friend of mine.

I do love Toblerone, especially the original and white chocolate varieties, the sea salt (blue one) maybe not so much. Whereas I still enjoyed it, it was kinda gritty, strangely reminiscent of a mouthful of aquarium gravel (Yes, as a child, my weird self did sample a mouthful of the stuff). Whereas it lacked the algae growth, it still clicked and clanged around my mouth a little more than I was comfortable with. I would certainly buy this product again, but I would probably give the blue one to a friend or family member who enjoyed it more than I.

The chocolate was shipped in what was supposed to be a cold pack. The box had a foil lining and there were 2 jell ice packs inside. I don't know the exact temperature inside the box, but it was probably over 101°. The jell ice packs were very warm to the touch. It felt more like the temperature you would want for a bath. I immediately placed the package of chocolate in the refrigerator. For the most part the chocolate maintained the triangular shape except at one end. About 2 inches of the chocolate was severely misshapen because of melting. I would order this again, but not in the summer months.

Absolutely awesome Swiss chocolates, 3 each of 3 varieties in 9 packages.  These are long, unusually shaped triangular bars containing honey and almonds, 3 of which are white chocolate (far and away my wife's favorite), 3 of milk chocolate, and 3 more of milk chocolate with some caramelized confection in it as well, each of which can be sub-divided into around 10 to 15 (?) easy to break-off, individual pieces if wanted, and every bar, hunk, individual piece or tiny bite of which is scrumptious. :-)  A bit expensive for nine chocolate bars, but the old saw about getting exactly that for which you pay seems once more to have been proved true.  Excellent chocolates and a wonderful treat for extra-special celebrations and the commonplace, everyday sort of situation you want to make special.  Yum!
Toblerone is amazing, but this is a great mix of different flavors, not just the standard milk chocolate one. The big triangle tube is a great gift too.

This item is beautiful, visually. Opening a Toblerone always reminds me of The Chocolate Factory. This packaging is pretty and clever. But what impressed me with this purchase is how it came in the box. I will say it was overdone but it does show the care on how the product gets to the buyer. It came sandwiched between 2 ice packs. The ice packs were wrapped in foam so they would not damage the look or shape of the product. The box is covered in foil on the inside; I'm guessing for temp control.Impressive. Delicious.Maybe just one ice pack is enough? I'm not complaining. I will buy it again. Saved the ice packs in my freezer. Will reuse.

When you first look at it you think as a chocolate lover there's not much there, nine bars. However, when you start eating it's so rich you can't finish a bar in one sitting. It has been a month and I still havey Chocolate, part of each flavor and 2 and half whole bars oftheother chocolate flavor. Even eating my most favorite I still have some of that one left too. I only want a few bites even on my highest craving days! Well Worth the cost, not many chocolates are like that!

Tasty but wouldn't advise ordering during the summer.  Only 76°f today and these were liquidized, even despite their care in shipping the Toblerones with a couple deluxe icepacks which had thawed.Turns out mostly fine if you pop them in the freezer after receiving delivery, although a bit of an ordeal to peal the resolidified chocolate off the inner foil wrapping.Strongly advise waiting until fall/winter to order.

This nine 3.52 ounce bar assortment of Toblerone candy includes three varieties—traditional milk chocolate with honey nougat, white chocolate with honey nougat along with milk chocolate with honey nougat and caramelized almonds.A product of Switzerland, each variety has the iconic triangular shape with 12 segments per bar. The group of nine bars are contained in a triangular shape carton making for a distinctive presentation.The milk chocolate is flavorful, not waxy or tasteless and the white chocolate has an excellent vanilla taste and both create delicious combinations with the honey nougat and caramelized almonds. Also, the inclusions are small bits so while they add some texture do not detract from the creamy milk/white chocolate.A four segment serving has 180 calories which is approximately the equivalent of a regular candy bar. Of course the shape of the segments makes it easy to simply break-off a segment or two which may be enough to satisfy a chocolate craving.To estimate shelf-life the Best Before date is 7 months in the future but dates may vary. Excellent.

Wow!Toblerone is a chocolate maker that is just special.  Quality and ingredients aside, there is just something cool about the bars shaped like triangular prisms.  It makes it more exotic - worthy of an event or just perfect for a small celebration because you've earned it.  I've never tried any of the varieties beyond the standard milk chocolate, and this variety pack has knocked my socks off.Each bar contains 3 servings, so do take that into account when you look at the price point.  One thing that was a bit of a surprise was the term "nougat;" normally, I associate that with something a bit gooey.  That sensation is absent here, but you do get little crispy bits that are nice.I'm not a huge fan of white chocolate, so that one is not for me.  The two milk chocolate varieties are both wonderful!  These would make fantastic gifts, and I would absolutely buy them for Easter baskets or stocking stuffers for next year.  So much better than those cheap waxy chocolate bunnies or Santas!

This is truly some of the best chocolate I have ever tried. Toblerone is creamy, rich, and delicious. I have tried all three varieties in this pack, and while I think the sea salt almond is my favorite, I truly love them all!The chocolate is parceled into pyramid-shaped pieces, and 4 pieces is 1 serving. I can just have one, though, and it is enough to satisfy me. My family approves, too, and there's something for everyone, as I have a family member who loves white chocolate and another who loves the more original chocolate. Nothing about this chocolate tastes artificial or stale - it's all very fresh.These bars would make for great gifts or little prizes. It's also something nice to keep on hand for when a chocolate craving hits. I recommend giving these a try - you'll just be sorry you didn't try them sooner!

I don't eat Toblerone often, but when I do, O.M.G. is the first thing that I have to say to this product. This product BLOWS Hershey chocolate away. Whether it be this product or the white chocolate, this stuff is seriously addictive. It's a great treat and the breakdown of the chocolate bar allows you to take a few pieces at a time to make a nightly treat instead of a one time sitting!

This is a wonderful assortment of what Toblerone has to offer. The original milk is always excellent, but I also really enjoy the salted caramel almond (blue sleeve) for a tasty twist on the original with the same smooth and melty milk chocolate, but with more of a crunch. White chocolate isn’t my favorite, but my family likes it a lot. It’s worth noting that the nougat is not creamy or soft, but rather it’s on the crunchier side and is almost like a toffee, which I love. Since you get 3 of each flavor, this assortment is great to hand out to family and friends for Valentine’s day, use as stocking stuffers, or for birthday treats (or just for yourself)! They’re all very fresh (good for at least 6 months), and simply delicious!

I love chocolate and have a major sweet tooth.  Much of my life I have stuck with the classic Hershey bars but lately I have decided to try other brands.  This is DELICIOUS!This is a variety pack that contains 3 Milk Chocolate bars, Chocolate bars, 3 White Chocolate bars, and 3 Swiss Milk Chocolate with Salted Caramelized Almond Chocolate bars.  The Salted Almond bars were my favorite as they are an amazing and perfect mix of salty and sweet with a tiny bit of crunch.  I have never eaten a more perfect chocolate bar.The chocolate itself is amazing.  It is creamy and not overly rich.  I could eat it all day and probably not feel sick.  It just tastes like luxury chocolate!

Toblerone is a pretty classic chocolate brand, well-known for its distinctive triangular shape. This particular gift set takes triangles to the next level by packaging nine triangular candy bars into an even bigger triangular box. Each bar contains smooth chocolate with some crunchy nougat bits interspersed in there. The classic bar, in the yellow package, has a milk chocolate base. The other variants in this variety pack include white chocolate and milk chocolate with almonds. I have a special fondness for the white chocolate version, but all of them are of course yummy. The milk chocolate is a true classic, and the almond version kicks it up a notch.

This gift set is a very nice set for any chocolate aficionado, and especially those who love Toblerone like I do. The unique Pyramid shape is pretty neat and holds 9 Toblerones, 3 classic ones, 3 white chocolate and 3 crunchy salted almond ones.The only one missing really is the dark chocolate one which is by far my favorite but not everyone likes the dark chocolate.What I really like about Toblerone is the nougat pieces inside each chocolate piece which gives it a unique taste.Overall, unless you absolutely need to have the dark chocolate flavors, this is a beautiful gift pack which gets a 5 stars from me.
I wished someone gifts me this chocolate in the future. It's so delicious. Sadly the package came undone however none of the chocolate came damaged.
This is a pretty great gift set for any chocolate lover. The packaging is fun, the chocolate is very tasty, and it comes with a nice variety so you can mix up the flavors.

I really enjoyed this gift set and would recommend it to anyone that likes Toblerones! The original flavor is, well, the original flavor. The taste is nice, but the there is something so captivating about breaking those little triangles apart. The white chocolate one was my favorite. I am NOT a fan of white chocolate in general, but I found this to be the perfect combination of sweet and salty. The salted caramel version was probably the sweetest and furthest from the traditional toblerone flavor, but offered the most complex flavor and I really enjoyed it also. The triangle shaped packaging that they came in was a cute idea. This set is super gift-able and created a lot of joy in our household. I would definitely recommend!

I thought that I had already received these. Since the other boxes we'd ordered had already been consumed, I was pleasantly surprised when these were delivered today.I love Toblerone. I ate it as a child and I was so excited to see it available. I love the smooth and creamy taste but I also like shape and the packaging. It's like when your food is artfully plated. It just makes it all that much more enjoyable.  It's yummy! This was a nostalgic treat. The variety of flavors was an added bonus. This packaging would make this a really neat added goody with a gift for someone.
Delicious gift for my parents. Too bad it arrived so late.
Extremely happy with the shipping the way it was packed with ice to keep the chocolate 🍫 from melting. Chocolate is delicious. Thank you so much…

The packaging for these bars is very cute. They come in a triangular box made to look like one giant Toblerone. Each bar is three serving sizes.Milk Chocolate bars: These have almond and honey nougat. They’re the crunchy and good classic bar.White Chocolate bars: These are good. The sweetness of them makes it easier to eat only a portion of these without overdoing it.Milk Chocolate with Salted Caramelized Almond: These were my favorite out of the set. They’re sweet and salty—the best of both worlds.

I have the 9 bar “Chocolate Variety” set that contains individually wrapped bars in 3 different flavors. You can tell that a lot of attention to detail goes into the packaging for this product because it’s well put together. Even better is that this chocolate tastes really good. The set includes white chocolate, milk chocolate and dark chocolate varieties, and they are all delicious. I like that the nut pieces are very small, so they blend well with the other flavors in the candy. This would make a nice gift for chocolate lovers!

This chocolate is delicious. It's rich and creamy. My favorite is the white chocolate but they are all so good! The bars come in little triangles making it easy to break a piece off for a cheat snack. I was a little worried about the almond but it gives it just the right amount of crisp. It's kind of like a crunch bar and not overpowering at all! These were gone in a week so it was a hit in my house!

I mean...not too much I can say...it's Toblerone. Delicious.I still like the original flavor the most, but the salted caramelized almond was tasty as well.I'm not a fan of white chocolate, so those were a no for me. If you don't like white chocolate either, get a different set or make sure you know someone that does like it. My husband happily ate the white chocolate ones for me.

I did not experience any of the problems which seem to have affected other reviewers.  My bars are the correct size (3.52oz. each) and the best buy date is not until October 2021.All three flavors are absolutely delicious and taste exactly as I expected them to.  The quality of Toblerone chocolate has not degraded over the years!

I got the correct size with an expiration 7 months away.Some of the best chocolate I’ve ever had. So easy to eat a whole bar even though one is quite large. The chocolate is creamy and delicious. None of the bars were broken. The best is the crunchy salted almond followed by the white chocolate. I loved how they melt in your mouth.
Toblerone is my favorite chocolate EVER!  Every single one of these were fresh and delicious!

I think the crunchy salted almond are the winners on this set, the original and white chocolate are good -- but I think I had fonder memories of them than the reality.  Really fun gift set, all packaged up in a larger triangle.

Bought this because I love the salted almond kind, and wanted to try the white.  The white did /not/ disappoint, I need more.They ship this super well.  You'll be getting two free ice packs with your order!  By the time I got it, the ice packs were melted, but still fairly cold.  Chocolate was pristine.  Might be a bit wasteful to ship this way, but the results speak for themselves.  A+.

Product was packaged in an insulated box with cold packs but I live in California and it’s triple digits here so they came melted and the ice packs were burning hot. So if you live in a hot climate I would pass on this lol some were still edible when we just put them in the freezer. Some had foil mashed into the chocolate so those couldn’t be eaten. Great chocolate though!

I was nervous ordering a box of chocolate in the middle of August online, but I was wildly impressed with the shipment packaging!It had a nice insulated box with ice packs packaged inside to help keep the chocolates from melting!Very sweet/above and beyond!If I'm ever needing more Toblerone I'll be coming back here, guaranteed 🤤

These came from Canada and I live in the US. I really didn’t expect these to arrive so well-shipped and in such a timely manner! I have never tried the salted and white chocolate Toblerones before so I took a chance. I’m so glad I did. These are SO DELICIOUS but so bad for my waistline. Ugh!

Product is delicious. Nice gift design.  Packaging was good. Except UPS kept it over a extremely hot weekend and the freeze bag melted all over product and soaked individual packs. Was able to save product by putting in freezer. What was savable tasted great

After putting off purchasing this product for almost six months, I finally pulled the trigger. Wish I’d have done it sooner. This chocolate is AWESOMESAUCE! Three flavors to choose from and each one is amazing on its own. Buy with confidence.
I didt received a gift set, and different types of chocolate just the regular one in a box, its the chocolate which was good, but no as described

This is one of my favorites. I have to give it a 4 star because they were somewhat melted upon delivery by my local USPS office. I threw them in the fridge and now they seem fine. I can consume lots of chocolate so I won't have any issue with the bars going bad.Lastly, these bars are shipped from PA and I live in CA. That could be the reason why they were a bit softer than they should have been.
A quality product, and seemed to be fresh & well packaged.

Toblerone bars have been a traditional part of our Christmas stockings for at least 35 years.  In addition to being a tradition, they are a family favorite.  I ordered these this year because it clearly stated that it was a 12 pack which made it quite a bargain.  However unlike advertised, it was a 6 pack and definitely not a bargain.  Several other places on the Amazon site plus local stores have six packs for less than what they are charging.  It is even possible to purchase six individual bars for less.  Very disappointed not in the product but in the misinformation.  Sellers can charge what they want and buyers can make their decisions as to what they will purchase.  But sellers should not be allowed to mislead consumers.  I definitely expect more integrity from companies that sell their products through Amazon.

Very good chocolate. But a little disappointed that I did not receive a box of them as shown in the image. The seller did send individual ones wrapped in bubble wrap... very disappointing.But hey, the chocolate taste good, the other thing I am not impressed is that it melt quite fast in the mouth (yum) but you are left with this sorta caramel (not sure what it is) like thing in your mouth that feels like plastic. I always spit it out but it dissolves if you are persistent :(

WOW! i could eat this chocolate all day. so im buying a pack of 12 :). id never think id be buying candy off amazon, but here i am, buying toblerone bars. but this chocolate is sooooo worthy of being purchased in bulk offline. i feel no need to search for a favorite chocolate bar anymore. no stomach aches after eating this. my stomach is sensitive to a lot of chocolates. not this! AND ITS AMAZING!

I knew they were melted before I even opened the box. And sure enough, they were! If anyone has ever had a toblerone, you know the signature shape in which they come and how they are stamped with the name on each triangle piece. It was even better than I remembered and tremendously better than the molded white chocolate bunnies or santas that I usually have to settle for around certain holidays.  The candy is shaped into connected, break apart triangles - which I love and makes for easy snacking.  Each bar, for me, is about two or three servings... Unless I'm being greedy :-)

TOBLERONE Tiny Swiss Chocolates Variety Pack - Milk Chocolate, Dark Chocolate & White Chocolate were so delicious! They are the perfect size for a small piece chocolate to curb a craving. All three of the flavors are equally mouth watering and flavorful.

Okay, guys, New Year's resolutions and all and I get a lovely sample of this chocolate in the mail. Not just one piece, or a few, but three boxes. Diet fail. Delicious chocolate, impossible to stay out of! The white chocolate is the BEST!

I was so excited to try these mini tolberon. My family was more excited though because they were gone 2 days after I got them. These tolberon candies came in white, dark and milk chocolate. I can't decide which one is my favorite . I love them all
I love the taste of these TOBLERONE Tiny Swiss Chocolates Variety Pack - Milk Chocolate, Dark Chocolate & White Chocolate! They all had a great taste and the shape of them were nice.

I'm very picky when it comes to chocolate and this chocolate is divine! It is super smooth and creamy and by far one of the best tasting chocolates I've ever had. I will be buying this again and again. I love it.

I have to say these are the BEST chocolates ever! They're the perfect size to snack on. I never knew about the mini's. Each flavor tastes amazing and I absolutely love the packaging. I recommend these to everyone.
perfect giveaway to friends, adults and kids alike, colleagues, whoever
Yummy treats. The small size makes you feel less guilty about eating them.

I am a true fan of the Toblerone line of chocolates, but was very pleased that they now make a miniature version called the Toblerone Tiny Swiss Chocolates Variety Pack. this wonder treat comes in dark, milk and white chocolates in this package and they really are as great as the full size chocolates. There is literally something for everyone in this pack. What a great treat for the whole family or to share. The package is unique and makes it great for gift giving as well. Grab yourself one to have on hand for a sweet treat, to gift or to share.

These are absolutely delicious and the perfect size for a little treat without going overboard. They are nice and creamy with the perfect amount of crunch. Everyone in my family loves them. My 2 year old is always begging for them, so we have to hide them. Definitely recommend these.

This Toblerone variety pack offers white chocolate, dark chocolate and milk chocolate. The white and dark are my favorites! The chocolate is smooth, rich and creamy. It completely satisfies my daily cravings and tastes delicious. I hadn't tried Toblerone in years, but will now be adding this to my shopping list- yum!

I love chocolate so much and was very excited to try the Toblerone variety. The tiny Toblerone are the perfect size and I take them everywhere I go because I am usually always looking for a sweet treat to snack on. I also love the triangle box it comes in, not only because it looks fancy and pretty, but because it sits perfectly on my desk and I can easily grab one when I want. Even at home, it fits perfect on my counters and because of the shape - it will not take up a lot of space. My favorites are the milk and white chocolate. The first bite starts to melt in your mouth and becomes super creamy. Then you start tasting the yummy flavors of the honey and almond nougat. The whole bite of chocolate tastes so fresh and so rich that you are am...

I have always wanted to try Toblerone, ever since seeing the episode of Friends when they grabbed some at the airport. Once it arrived, I was reading about it and how it is Swiss Chocolate and I could hardly wait since in my experience Swiss chocolate is some of the best. The presentation was nice, the box was unique but I was so disappointed in what I tasted. It tasted kind of stale, like old Halloween chocolate leftover months later in the bottom of a child's Halloween bucket. I have tried all three kinds that were in the box and shared with guests when they came to visit and they shared the same sentiments. Will not be buying any of this candy in the future.

Toblerone is my husband's all-time favorite chocolate so seeing these tiny versions was so exciting! He loved them as did my whole family. They are perfect for a candy dish or a quick treat. I already know I will be buying some for my family Easter baskets. Little mini versions of the original. So cute and delicious.
These chocolates are like No other. They are Super rich and extremely creamy. The tiny toffee bits are heavenly. I love the bite size since I can't eat more than one at a time.
I absolutely loved these chocolates! Typically, I do not care for dark chocolate. This brand is wonderful even my children loved it!
I didnt even know that these were available in mini sizes, much less assorted flavors!! These are perfect! My new ""go-to"" snacks!
These are the best chocolates. I like all three of them creamy and yummy and delicious
Huge, but 1 is still not enough. Lol
Put in the stockings this Xmas. A very tasty treat. They all enjoyed!
a family favorite! it doesn't last long around here. enjoy!
I love this candy! It's good as a gift or to eat yourself!
I’m from Europe and absolutely dislike American “chocolate”. This is a good buy for whenever I want a good tasting treat. The different shape makes it also more fun to eat. Makes a good gift.
We give these as Holiday gifts to our loved ones who enjoy chocolate. They gobble it up while they are visiting. No small feat. It is a substantial amount of chocolate. Very decadent. : )

What can I say?! My absolute favorite chocolate ever! It’s not the cheapest but it’s definitely the most delicious. I have to hold myself back from not eating the whole bar in one sitting.. who am I kidding, I don’t hold myself back lol, it’s always gone in 5 mins!
It’s fine. The price is not horrible, if you like the candy it’s a good deal. I recommend you keep it in the freezer while not eating.
This ain't a Toblerone.. this is a ToblerTWO!
Just like the one that you get from the airport.
Does not come as shown in the photo, but it comes as one large bar! It’s HUGE!
The label is missleading, you definitely only get one toblerlone bar, but it's pretty huge. My husband loves this candy bar so every year I get him one for Christmas. So delicious!!
If you’re a fan of toblerone then these are for you. It’s not as advertised though, this is the larger version which you get one of.
The product description is incorrect. This item only contains one bar, not 10.
Way larger than I thought it would be. My husband will love it!
this is not as pictured or described. this is for the GIANT 1 piece of candy. still delicious chocolate.

I liked it, I ate it, It's gone :(
New favorite chocolate! So smooth and creamy and the little pieces inside are so delicious! I saw it on Friends when I was little and always wanted to try it. Love it.
One of the best chocolates and I love the pieces of nougat inside, just makes your mouth water, thanks!!!
I couldn’t decided between the smaller and larger size. The larger size is worth the money.
It is one, larger than average Toblerone, not a box of them. This is a pretty good value for one this size, though.
Stocking stuffer for my husband, he loved it
Awesome chocolate, with no plastic in the wrapper.
My favorite chocolate to make chocolate ganache
Gave it to friend as a gift, didn’t realize it was just ONE giant bar.

Tolberone Swiss milk chocolate with honey and almond nougat is my weakness! I’m a chocolate snob after visiting Amish country in Pennsylvania. Love how Tolberone can be broken off into sections for portion control. Two thumbs up to Target for carrying quality chocolate!
Bought for gifts but had to keep a few for me!Fresh and delish-Target reps are terrific -very helpful!

at less than $6 this is less than half the price than at other stores. i was concerned because i thought this might be a cheaper version made in the USA but the box says it was made in Switzerland and it tastes fine. some might not be aware Toblerone recently reduced the size from 400 grams to 360, it breaks into 9 pieces now instead of 11. There was a big outcry about it in Britain. If it bothers you that much buy two. Disadvantage is once you get it in front of you you will probably eat it all.
Made for a great extra Christmas present to my husband who loves this chocolate!
Very nice gift for kids and for the family.thanks
Heavenly delicious, as always. The small chips of nuts make this a special treat.
My family loves to wake up Christmas morning to find this lucious chocolate in their stockings . Thanks for making this purchase so easy.
It was a nice gift for my son! He loved it. It took several days to eat it.
I had no idea they came this big,boy was I surprised for this treat!!! Took a week or two to finish 🥰🥰
Love this candy bar. It’s delicious!
This is such a delicious treat. I love how easy it is to break off a small piece, then wrap the end of the bar in the foil. It stays fresh. (Although we eat it pretty quick. ha!)

This has been my go to get away snack for some time now. I love that you can break off small individual pieces if you just want a little. The amount of nougat is perfect for me....just enough so it doesn't want to stick to your teeth. I add one of these to almost every order.
I like the balance of chocolate and honey. It’s a specific craving. But absolutely delicious.
I absolutely love this chocolate! The Honey and Almond peices are so good, they complement the Chocolate so well! I also love that its not too sweet
Best chocolate. Love this on a daily basis.
